Name: Skelecanth Tartare
AttributesDescription: Reduces Wall Dash and Swimming STA consumption for all Resonators in the team by 20% for 15m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: In the Royan language, the name of this dish means “sand-buried”—a reference to how the Roya preserve Skelecanth rinsed in salt and spice. During this slow process, the fish gently ferments, its flesh turning tender and deeply flavorful.
